metadata.desc: First symmetrical BRC20 & CBRC20 token, deployed on the same sat/inscription. Redefines efficiency by merging BRC20 & CBRC20 actions, saving fees.
metadata.name: Symmetry
metadata.purpose: Experimental, Inception-like 'token in token' design, allowing simultaneous deploy, mint, transfer of both token forms in a single inscription. Goodbye fees, hello MOTO.
